name: Infinitrack Anchor Drill
desc: When this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 EARTH Machine monster from your hand in Defense Position. You can target 1 other Machine monster you control; the Levels of that targeted monster and this face-up card become their combined original Levels, until the end of this turn. You can only use each effect of "Infinitrack Anchor Drill" once per turn.
